'''長鬚王蜥屬'''（[[学名|学名]]：''Barbaturex''）是一种已灭绝的食草[[鬣蜥亞目|鬣蜥]]，生存于[[始新世|始新世]]晚期（约3720万年前）的[[缅甸|缅甸]]，屬下只有[[單型|單種]]'''莫氏長鬚王蜥'''（''Barbaturex morrisoni''）。

==名稱起源==
長鬚王蜥屬的學名是拉丁詞「Barbatus」和「rex」的[[混成詞|混成詞]]，意即「有鬍鬚的王者」，因其下顎的突出物和龐大的體積而得名<ref name=Hetal13/>。至於屬下單種名稱中的「莫氏」（morrisoni）則指的[[門戶樂隊|門戶樂隊]]的主唱[[占·摩利臣|占·摩利臣]]，因他有「蜥蜴王」（The Lizard King）之稱<ref name="BBC News">{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-22764946 |title=Extinct lizard named after The Doors' singer Jim Morrison |accessdate=2013-06-06 |work=BBC News |archive-date=2018-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180601220342/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-22764946 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==特徵==
由莫氏長鬚王蜥的骨骼的大小可知，其吻肛距離約為1米<ref name=Hetal13>{{cite journal|title=Giant lizards occupied herbivorous mammalian ecospace during the Paleogene greenhouse in Southeast Asia|journal=Proc. R. Soc. B|date=2013-07-22|doi=10.1098/rspb.2013.0665|url=http://rspb.royalsocietypublishing.org/content/280/1763/20130665|language=en|volume=280|issue=1763|pages=20130665|issn=0962-8452|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Jason J. Head, Gregg F. Gunnell, Patricia A. Holroyd, J. Howard Hutchison, Russell L. Ciochon|archive-date=2018-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180714193206/http://rspb.royalsocietypublishing.org/content/280/1763/20130665|dead-url=no}}</ref>，延至尾部則有1.8米<ref name=ScienceDaily>{{cite news |title='Lizard King' Fossil Shows Giant Reptiles Coexisted With Mammals During Globally Warm Past |last=Smith |first=Steve |url=http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2013/06/130605090421.htm |newspaper=ScienceDaily |date=5 June 2013 |accessdate=5 June 2013 |archive-date=2017-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170519021743/https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2013/06/130605090421.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

